1. *U odnosu* na prošlu godinu, imamo manje posla. (In relation to last year, we have less work.)
2. Moramo pronaći *odgovarajući odnos* između rada i odmora. (We need to find an appropriate balance between work and rest.)
3. Ona je imala *loš odnos* sa svojim šefom. (She had a bad relationship with her boss.)
4. *Odnosno*, to znači da moramo napraviti izmjene u planu. (That is to say, we need to make some changes to the plan.)
5. *U odnosu* na konkurenciju, naša tvrtka je najuspješnija. (Compared to the competition, our company is the most successful.)
6. Naš *odnos prema* okolišu mora se poboljšati. (Our attitude towards the environment needs to improve.)
7. Ova knjiga pruža *dobar uvid u odnos između* umjetnosti i društva. (This book provides a good insight into the relationship between art and society.)
8. *U odnosu* na prethodni model, ovaj novi automobil ima više funkcija. (Compared to the previous model, this new car has more features.)
9. Njihov *odnos je* bio strastven ali nestabilan. (Their relationship was passionate but unstable.)
10. Pokušavamo uspostaviti *dobru poslovnu suradnju u odnosu na* naše partnere. (We are trying to establish good business cooperation with our partners.)